PLEASE!!!!!!! READ THIS BEFORE ASKING THINGS ON MY WHATTSAPP!

DO NO USE THE DISK AS A BACKUP. REMOVE ANYTHING THAT IS NOT BEING USED IN CALCULATIONS

* BASIC COMMANDS SLURM:
	sinfo                  : cluster/nodes status
	squeue                 : queue status
	scancel ID             : kills the job of number ID
	sbatch script.sh       : submits the job
	scontrol show jobid ID : gives a full report on a given job
	scancel -u username    : kill all your jobs

* COMMAND TO COPY FOLDERS TO YOUR LOCAL MACHINE:
	scp -r -P 80 user_name@IP:/path_remote/ /path_local/

* COMMAND TO COPY FILES TO YOUR LOCAL MACHINE:
	scp -P 80 user_name@IP:/path_remote/ /path_local/

NOTE1: The folder "CLUSTER_TEMPLATES" contains examples of numerous job submissions. 
NOTE2: DOT NOT CREATE DIRECTORIES WITH SPACE/SPECIAL CHARACTERS EX.: "ESTRUTURA ELETRÃ”NICA".

